Place refried beans into a bowl and mash until smooth. Scoop avocado out of the peels and mash with refried beans until thoroughly combined. Spread the bean mixture over a large platter in an even layer. Mix sour cream, mayonnaise, and taco seasoning in a bowl; spread in a layer over the bean mixture. Sprinkle tomatoes and green onions as a single layer, then top with a layer of bean sprouts. Sprinkle Cheddar cheese over the top.